      "text": "{user}さん、お休みなのに\n時間をいただいてすみません……",
      "startTime": 8.966666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "いいよ、俺も休日の方が時間が取れるし",
      "startTime": 12.066666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01-ai002.m4a",
      "text": "そう言っていただけると助かります……",
      "startTime": 16.066666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01-ai003.m4a",
      "text": "……ふぅ",
      "startTime": 19.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "今日は相談があるってことだけど……\nなんだか元気ないな。深刻なことなのか？",
      "startTime": 25,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01-ai004.m4a",
      "text": "い、いえ、{user}さんにとっては\nそんなに大したことじゃないんです！",
      "startTime": 31.866666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_01_01-ai005.m4a",
      "text": "ただ、ちょっと私……\n芸能界引退しようかなって……あはは……",
      "startTime": 36.8,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}